Register Today for a Chat with Sales

Email Encryption
Zix offers the industry’s leading email encryption solutions by combining a unique community approach with a Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) architecture. Zix Email Encryption is easy to install, easy to maintain and, most importantly, easy to use. For more information, visit: zixcorp.com/email-encryption.

Email Data Loss Prevention (DLP)
With email as simple as a click, it's easy to understand how employees could accidentally send a sensitive email to the wrong recipient or attach the wrong file. With ZixQuarantine, your organization can monitor and protect the channel that both assists your company in running efficiently and exposes your organization to the most risk. For more information, visit: zixcorp.com/dlp.

ZixOne for BYOD
ZixOne is a mobile app that simplifies the BYOD challenge by enabling easy access to email. With ZixOne, companies control access to corporate email without jeopardizing data protection or productivity, because corporate email never resides on the device. For more information, visit: zixcorp.com/byod.
To be directed to our homepage, please visit: zixcorp.com.


