Zix





















































Effortless Email Security.
With the right solutions, secure email can be as easy as regular email. Let us prove it.

Request a Free Trial



Superior Products
The challenge has never been greater, and the stakes have never been higher. You need to protect your customers, data, employees and company, and you need to do it without getting in their way. We get that, and we get email security. 

Nearly 19,000 businesses count on us for superior and effortless solutions. So while our customers endure an ever-increasing list of threats, one thing remains constant - their email is secure with Zix. Let us provide you the same peace of mind.



ZixEncryptZixProtectZixMailZixArchiveZixOne





ZixEncrypt

ZixEncrypt offers the industry’s most trusted solution for email encryption and a simplified solution for data loss prevention. Your employees simply click ‘send.’ ZixEncrypt does the rest.
Benefits:

Proven policies filters to automatically identify sensitive information and trigger email encryption or quarantine
Convenient delivery to anyone with an email address through our patented Best Method of Delivery
Seamless integration with hosted, on-premises and virtual email

Learn More





ZixProtect

Email is the top attack vector, containing malware, ransomware and other advanced threats that damage the health of your business. ZixProtect prevents email attacks to keep your business running.
Benefits:

Minimize email threats with 99.5% accuracy
Exceptional support from threat analysts who are dedicated to keeping you safe and happy
Seamless deployment with your infrastructre and easy integration with ZixEncrypt

Learn More





ZixMail

ZixMail provides end-to-end and internal encryption to protect emails and attachments with a single click.
Benefits:

Convenient integration with your current email system, and easy-to-use plug-ins for Outlook
Automatic key management with ZixDirectory, the world's largest email encryption community
Authentication with time-stamping of recipient delivery

  Learn More





ZixArchive

ZixArchive enables cloud-based control and access to retained emails, easing compliance and eDiscovery for you and your team.
Benefits:

Collect and store as many emails as needed for as long as needed
Manage policies and wildcarding to define what emails are retained
Maintain control of your data by easily enabling and disabling access priveleges

Learn More





ZixOne

ZixOne delivers the promises of BYOD without compromising data security by offering a no-data-on-the-device approach.
Benefits:

Enhanced productivity with convenient access to work email through an intuitive app
Improved security and compliance by not allowing email data to reside on the device
Protection of employee privacy and reduced liability without access to personal devices

Learn More





























